6/29/83 forum request: next

Syntax:  next {trans_spec} {-control_args}


Syntax as an active request:  [next {trans_spec} {-control_args}]


Function:
Prints or returns the transaction index of the transaction after the
specified transaction, or after the current transaction if no
trans_spec is given.


Arguments:
trans_spec
   is the transaction for which the next tranaction is desired.


Control arguments:
-include_deleted, -idl
   print or return the index of the next transaction even if it is 
   deleted.
-only_deleted, -odl
   print or return the index of the next deleted transaction.
-only_non_deleted, -ondl
   print or return the index of the next non-deleted transaction.
   (Default)
